542
00:29:14.286 --> 00:29:16.487
<font color="#ffff000">We have to stop him before he hurts anyone else.</font>
Chúng ta phải ngăn chặn hắn trước khi hắn làm hại đến ai khác nữa.

543
00:29:16.489 --> 00:29:18.322
<font color="#ffff000">Barry!</font>
Barry!

544
00:29:18.324 --> 00:29:19.556
<font color="#ffff000">That's a job for the police.</font>
